---

<section class="product-section">
  <div class="wrap product">
    <div class="product__media">
      <div class="phone-frame">
        <div class="phone-frame__notch"></div>
        <div class="phone-frame__screen">
          <img
            src="/screenshots/app-mobile-screenshot-4.jpeg"
            alt="Pantalla de inicio de INOUT con el balance total del mes"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="callout callout--in">
          <span class="pip pip--green"><i data-lucide="trending-up"></i></span>
          <span>+S/&nbsp;1,200.00</span>
        </div>
        <div class="callout callout--out">
          <span class="pip pip--red"><i data-lucide="trending-down"></i></span>
          <span>&minus;S/&nbsp;728.50</span>
        </div>
        <div class="callout callout--cat">
          <span class="pip pip--navy"><i data-lucide="layers"></i></span>
          <span>Ritmo de gasto</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow-row">Tu pantalla principal</div>
      <h2 class="section__h2 product__title">
        Tu mes entero,<br />de un vistazo.
      </h2>
      <p class="section__lead">
        Una tarjeta resumen, un numero grande y lo justo debajo: ingresos,
        gastos y neto del mes. Sin graficos confusos ni gamification
        innecesaria, solo claridad.
      </p>

      <div class="feature-list">
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature__icon navy"><i data-lucide="wallet"></i></div>
          <div>
            <h3>Tu balance, siempre arriba</h3>
            <p>
              Balance total, ingresos, gastos y neto del mes en una sola
              tarjeta. Lo primero que ves al abrir la app.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature__icon green"><i data-lucide="gauge"></i></div>
          <div>
            <h3>Ritmo de gasto del mes</h3>
            <p>
              INOUT proyecta cuanto vas a gastar a fin de mes segun tu ritmo
              actual. Te avisa antes de que sea tarde.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature__icon"><i data-lucide="shapes"></i></div>
          <div>
            <h3>En que gastaste, ordenado</h3>
            <p>
              Cada gasto cae en una categoria con nombre humano y color. Ves al
              instante a donde se fue la mayor parte.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .product-section {
    padding-top: clamp(72px, 9vw, 120px);
    background: var(--color-cream-2);
  }
  .product {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.05fr;
    gap: clamp(40px, 6vw, 96px);
    align-items: center;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .product {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .product__media {
    position: relative;
  }
  .product__title {
    font-size: clamp(34px, 4.4vw, 58px);
  }

  .phone-frame {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 340px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    aspect-ratio: 9 / 19.5;
    background: var(--color-navy);
    border-radius: 46px;
    padding: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-ink-12);
    box-shadow: 0 28px 70px rgba(20, 19, 14, 0.16);
  }
  .phone-frame__notch {
    position: absolute;
    top: 22px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 95px;
    height: 24px;
    background: var(--color-navy);
    border-radius: 999px;
    z-index: 3;
  }
  .phone-frame__screen {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 38px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--color-cream);
  }
  .phone-frame__screen img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top center;
  }

  .callout {
    position: absolute;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: var(--color-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-ink-12);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 8px 14px 8px 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    white-space: nowrap;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(20, 19, 14, 0.1);
  }
  .callout .pip {
    width: 26px;
    height: 26px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
  }
  .callout :global(.lucide) {
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
  }
  .pip--green {
    background: var(--color-green);
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .pip--red {
    background: var(--color-red);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }
  .pip--navy {
    background: var(--color-navy-2);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .callout--in {
    left: -26px;
    top: 16%;
    animation: inout-float 6s var(--ease-in-out) infinite;
  }
  .callout--out {
    right: -26px;
    top: 38%;
    animation: inout-float 6.4s var(--ease-in-out) 0.3s infinite;
  }
  .callout--cat {
    left: -16px;
    bottom: 20%;
    animation: inout-float 6.8s var(--ease-in-out) 0.6s infinite;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .callout--in {
      left: 0;
    }
    .callout--out {
      right: 0;
    }
    .callout--cat {
      left: 8px;
    }
  }

  .feature-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 36px;
  }
  .feature {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: start;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-ink-12);
  }
  .feature:first-child {
    border-top: 0;
    padding-top: 0;
  }
  .feature__icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    background: var(--color-cream);
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .feature__icon.green {
    background: var(--color-green);
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .feature__icon.navy {
    background: var(--color-navy);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }
  .feature__icon :global(.lucide) {
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    stroke-width: 2;
  }
  .feature h3 {
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    margin: 0 0 6px;
  }
  .feature p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--color-ink-60);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
</style>
